svg.metadata: Created by FontForge 20170924 at Fri Jan 20 14:14:33 2012 By Glenn,,, Sonsie One is a heavy, medium contrast, large x height script font. It was inspired by hand painted signs seen in Munich. Sonsie One improves on its sources by adding warmth, smoother flow and of touch of funkiness. Sonsie One is best used for display purposes at medium to large sizes.
